SQL_STMT_U.val: select T.hr_x_ep_in_out, T.hr_x_datetimein, T.hr_x_msgtype, T.hr_x_epmsgseqnum, I.i_xml_messsage from HR_HEADER T, INKOMEND_XML I where I.i_xml_epmsgseqnum = T.hr_x_epmsgseqnum and I.i_xml_msgtype = T.hr_x_msgtype and ~1 in ('I', 'I/O') and T.hr_x_berichtverwerkt=1 and ( ~2=' ' OR INSTR(~2, T.hr_x_msgtype )<>0 ) and substr(T.hr_x_datetimein, 1, 8) between ~4 and ~5 UNION ALL select T.hr_x_ep_in_out, T.hr_x_datetimein, T.hr_x_msgtype, T.hr_x_epmsgseqnum, u.u_xml_messsage from HR_HEADER T, UITGAAND_XML U where u.u_xml_epmsgseqnum = T.hr_x_epmsgseqnum and u.u_xml_msgtype = T.hr_x_msgtype and T.hr_x_procesid=1 and ~1 in ('O', 'I/O') and T.hr_x_berichtverwerkt=1 and ( ~3=' ' OR INSTR(~3, T.hr_x_msgtype )<>0 ) and substr(T.hr_x_datetimein, 1, 8) between ~4 and ~5
